title: Mozart, Schubert - Music for Two Pianos - Perahia, Lupu
description:
Mozart: Sonata for Two Pianos in D major, K. 448 &
Schubert : Fantasia for Piano, Four Hands in F minor, D 940.

Both of these pieces, recorded in 1984 by Murray Perahia and Radu Lupu, are meant for two performers at either one or two pianos, unaccompanied. They are beautiful performances and recordings. This CD was reissued by Sony in 1992.

Please enjoy.
